          "reviewBody": "a. English communication skill is very very poor.\nb. Teachers often write the answer in the book sheet without explaining the way to solve the problem.\nc. Opportunity needs to be given to all the students.\nd. Concepts of Maths in small is very poor.\ne. fundamental teaching is poor.\nf. School fee is higher compare to the other schools.\ng. Most of the good teachers and top students  are leaving the school\n",
