          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As a Parent I would say, Sairam Vidyalaya providing the best platform for students.The school is not the same before 4years. After the new senior principal joined, lot many changes are incorporated in the school positively.\nFirstly,play area is important thing that every school must have.He renovated the school back side in to play ground where students are very happy for their sports activities.\nRegarding club activities: Many technical as well as Extra curricular related Clubs are introduced. Through this the kids are engaging informatively after school hours.\nThe wonderful concept called Seven habits were introduced for the kids beginning from Kg level. This is an excellent initiative. Seven habits programme was conducted for parents too.\nI attended the same and it was very informative. Corporate level objectives and approach were inculcated in our kids at earlier stage itself. This will definitely enhance them in future.The foremost thing is both teachers and principal are always approachable.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
