            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As a parent , I really appreciate Sairam management teachers senior principal and all staffs for arranging Seven habits Programme for parents. It was very useful and we came to learn many useful ways to engage with kids, how to handle kids in a better way from their world, The way Doctor spoke was really awesome and Thanks a lot for doctor too….\n\nNext afternoon session was again a very useful one how to take care of ourselves both physically and mentally. It clearly explains how to live a life in a very efficient manner and how to become successful and lead a happy life. We will follow these values in our day to day life. Thanks a lot for the management and all parents are very thankful for cultivating these values from our small kids too….",
